Mkulu woyang'anira sukuluyo a Luc Deschamps anati "ndikofunukira kusangalala khilisimasi chifukwa anawa alibe makolo awo."
Iwowa amakhala ndi agogo awo kapena amalume, azakhali achibale chapatali ndipo samakwanitsa kusangalala kwawo kapena kuchita phwando nadya ma suwiti ndi ma keke. Ndiye timakonza tsiku lachisangalalo kwa anawa kuti asangalale khilisimasi
Palibe umboni wochokera ku nyumba zofalitsa nkhani.
