A Milanzi anati pochepetsa ntchito yosenza madzi osamba kupita nawo kwawo, azimayi amasankha kusamba mu mtsinjewo. Koma anati amasokonezedwa ndi achinyamata omwe amabisala mu tchire lapafupi.
